[signal arg="c3s1_entered"]
[signal arg="debug_character_check"]
[background arg="res://Bg/courtyard.png" fade="1.0"]
[voice path="res://assets/audio/voice/Chapter 3/c3s1/Art Week..mp3" volume=50 bus="Voice"]
Art Week. The courtyard buzzes with excitement as students gather around colorful displays.
[voice path="res://assets/audio/voice/Chapter 3/c3s1/Paintings line the walls..mp3" volume=50 bus="Voice"]
Paintings line the walls. Sculptures stand on pedestals. The air smells of fresh paint and possibility.
[wait time="0.1"]
[signal arg="debug_before_conditional"]
if {selected_character} == "celestine":
	join Celestine (half) left
	join Mark (Mark_half) right
	Mark: Man, after the exam sabotage and the missing fund... it's nice to have something normal for once.
	Celestine: "Normal" is relative. But yes, this is refreshing...
	Mark: Two cases solved. You're getting quite the reputation, you know.
	Celestine: I'm just following the evidence. Anyone could do it.
	Mark: Not anyone has a mysterious spirit guide helping them.
	[voice path="res://assets/audio/voice/Chapter 3/c3s1/Conrad shoots Mark.mp3" volume=50 bus="Voice"]
	Celestine shoots Mark a warning look.
	Celestine: Keep your voice down.
	Mark: Relax, no one's listening. They're all too busy with the art.
	[voice path="res://assets/audio/voice/Chapter 3/c3s1/Mark gestures.mp3" volume=50 bus="Voice"]
	Mark gestures at the colorful displays surrounding them.
	Mark: Speaking of which - have you seen Mia's sculpture? The one that won regionals?
	Celestine: "The Reader"? I've heard it's the centerpiece of the exhibit.
	Mark: Let's check it out. Everyone's been talking about it.
	Celestine: Lead the way.
else:
	join Conrad (half) left
	join Mark (Mark_half) right
	Mark: Man, after the exam sabotage and the missing fund... it's nice to have something normal for once.
	Conrad: "Normal" is relative. But yes, this is refreshing...
	Mark: Two cases solved. You're getting quite the reputation, you know.
